Have a safe weekend, talk to yo all Monday, I have tons to update about and I wont be working anymore so I'll have some extra time.

Ok this is hell, pure freaking hell, for those of you on my friends list that arent local friends too, let me just tell you it is 107 degrees here in Fresno Freaking California, and being that im bout 8 mths pregnant that means that I am like 701 degrees, im gonna fucking croak. 
MUST SWIMMMMMMMMMM
Well my company is going outta business, so I'll be having no job, ackkkk, scarry shit. I am going to apply at some portrait studios after the baby is born, that is the one thing I loved to do and im pretty damn good at it, if I might say so myself,hehe. I have to update my portfolio though, it is over 5 years old, I havent done pictures since Lou was 1 year old, my goodness.
I am poor right now, and so sick of being poor, and with new baby on the way it really sucks. I cant even afford the necessities, but im not letting that get me down.
I have registered at (The Lulliby Club at Target, and Babies R Us, and Walmart for baby stuff) I dont wanna push an online baby shower on any of yall, so if anyone wants (and I truley mean WANTS, no pressure) to buy the baby something for the shower let me know and I'll give you the links.
And for my Lo's and Lette's out there (It will all be explained in the book) You mean the book that is coming out in 3 days???? Yup that be the one, whoop whoop. I cant afford it so who ever wants to burn it for me that would be mighty kind of you,lol. I heard psrts of it on the sample on their site, and DIZAAAAM, that shit is tight.
Well im gonna jam, so hope everyone has a fun, safe, cool, tight, sick, dope weekend.
LUVINS ALL

Looks like im gonna have a daughter, she is still breech so the doctor is going to wait till July 22nd and if she doesnt flip (she has been in this position for 3 mths) then they will try to turn her over and if she still wants to be stubborn then I will be having a C-section (SCARRY). Here's her face, hope the cut works cause the picture is kinda big. Contractions have stopped so that lil scare is over (knock on wood). But here is a little taste of my biggest scare, regarding Louie. He had the MRI/MRA done Monday, he was loaded, he kept trying to fight with himself in the mirror and he kept telling me that the guy in the mirror wouldnt stop staring at him,lol, I dont like seeing my son all high like that but it was comical. They found a blood clot in the artery of his arm which is why it has been so cold and if it doesnt push the clot through itself they will schedule a bypass. We will know more within the next few weeks, I'll let you all know when I find out. I want to thank you all for being so supportive of me, I really appreciate your genuine concern, it means alot. So as usual, tons of stuff, very little time, and trying to stay sain through it all.

You are a goddess!

I thought in case any of you were wondering about the syndrome that Lou has you can find very good info on it here. Which lets me know even more that the doctor should have recognized the symptoms one of the 4 times in the first week that I took him back. Check it out:
http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/001224.htm
http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/001221.htm
Candice

Turns out that the entire time I was complaining that something was wrong after the break, and was told that his swelling and excruciating pain was normal, was all bull shit. He had a condition that is called ISCHEMIC COMPARTMENT SYNDROME and it was a condition that, if caught in time, like the 4 times that I took him back complaining, that it could have been fixed. But rather than the Dr. take the time to cover all the possibilities that could have been causing such pain and discomfort he brushed us off as overprotective parents, and now my baby has to have surgery again(by another doctor) to see if they can fix some of the damage, and if it is successful he may gain 50% usage of his hand again. Fucking 50% is an optimistic estimate he says. You know how hard it is to hear that? I am fucking breaking down. He will pay for this, he treated us like we were idiots and blamed my son's stiffness on him being a baby about it, he was wrong and he will pay. His bosses were there for todays appointment and they have sent a referral to the plastic surgeon and to the patients advocates office because they know they are being suid now, damn right they are, they will pay for him loosing a part of his life because of their neglagance.
He said SORRY. SORRY? Sorry doesnt give my 6-year-old his hand back. I am having to teach him how to do things with one hand, like tie his shoe, and he is a trooper about it but it is alot of work, and it is hard for him to have to go to therapy 3 times a week while his friends do fun things like ride a bike and climb trees, it isnt fair. Yes I am greatful that he is alive and that he can walk and talk and breathe, but if not for this ass holes cocky attitude and neglagance my son would be capable of tying his shoes by himself today so for that he will pay.
I told Lou that will will prove them wrong, and that he will use his hand again and it will be better than before, and he takes that like a tough lil guy and agrees, but he is scared. Last time he had surgery he went through excruciating pain and it was avoidable so I understand why it scares him. We will get through this, but rest assure, he will have 4-6 years of college paid for, and he will have money to buy a brand new car when he groes up among other things. He will be compinsated for this.
Im tired. Thats all.
Hope you all are ok, sorry for the crazy lady post, but im still pretty much feeling that way about my ex so I wont even start on that one. This day makes it even harder, it would be cool to not have to go through this alone, but fuck it, I,we'll be fine.
Luvs to you all

Mom didnt have blood pressure med for three days and couldnt get outta bed due to the fact that she looked like a blow fish, my sister went and got it for her and left Brittney there to run amuck through the house so I stopped by on my way home from work, I was hella freaking tired and so was Lou and we still had his homework, dinner, 2 loads of laundry and "that 70's show at 8,lol all to get done and it was already like 7pm, FUCK. I gotta get control of this hectic shit. When I was at Moms Lou was being a tired, crabby lil guy and so I was all "kiss grandma, were going home" and as he walked into her room to tell her goodbye he trips causing all her wanna be dogs (lil chiuahas) to yalp hystarically which drowned out Lou's tears cause he caught himself with his left arm coming down and it hurt which poostponed anything we had to get done last night cause I was trying to make him feel better, I think the fact that it hurt a little was the worst part cause it is just a reminder to him that he is nt all normal right now, so tears lasted a WHILE.

So Junior and Jelly show up pretty thrashed around 10:00, Both staggering all over the place, fucking idiots knocked my playstation off the entertainment center along with everything that was sitting in front of it. I yelled at them like a billion times to shut the fuck up cause Lou was sleeping. Then D calls and bitches me out for letting them in when they have been drinking,but wont even speak to him when he does, duh dude, difference being they dont kick my ass. But they just stayed till they could get their stroll on to some lil tricks of theirs house, till round 11:00, then I locked my door and crashed.

Im so glad it is almost the end of the week. Like the weekends are even near a relaxation time, but at least I dont gotta work.
I counted how many times I wake up during the night, last night it was 5 times, no wonder im so tired.

I want Ice cream.

I am having a mental fucking breakdown. I just dont know anymore. I am  scared outta my fucking mind, I dont want to be alone, I dont want to be with Dustin (although it would have been nice) because I dont want to get hurt physically or emotionally anymore, but im so fucking tired of trying to handle everything by myself. Yeah I got myself into this, I know, and I love my son and I love my baby, but it was never suppose to be like this. I can talk all the shit in the world and say how tough I am and how strong I am but ya know what? I cant even lift the laundry basket without loosing my breath and feeling like im going ot pass out. Fuck this. Then he wants to say that I should just be with him, that he loves me and forget about the past, even though he is still the exact person from the past that he swore he would never be again. It would be so easy to just say ok, and then I would have a black eye to be crying about instead of just a broken, lonely heart. I sometimes wonder which is worse. My brain is fucked, I cant stop crying, I want my Mom to take care of me but im  the Mom now, it just isnt suppose to be like this. I hate admitting that I cant hang, and that I dont know what to do. I just need someone to take over for me. 
The world is so big, and im such a small peice of it, why did I make such bad decisions? Why cant I be that girl that got lucky and found her Mr.Wright, and he loves her and they have a happy little fucking family togather? Why couldnt I be her. Im not a bad person. It is one thing after another, and I just want my turn to rest, I just want out.

I had a couple of perks, but for the most part i feel kinda crappy. My throat hurts really bad, and although I know how much of a wuss I am when it comes to the discomfort of not feeling perfectly healthy I really feel bad. I have tried to snap outta it, drank juice instead of soda, ate salad instead of fast food, and tried to go for walk instead of just lying my head down on my desk but I still feel like crap, this is the last of it though, cause I have been feeling it coming on for like 3 days now and today so far is the worse yet.

I have read some sad shit today too which makes for a depressing ass mood set, so enough of that shit. Lou is staying at his Dad's tonight, which is cool cause my Dad is going over there for dinner, (I know sounds weird huh?) I grew up with my son's dad and while I wouldnt choose to keep him as a buddy ol pal if not for my son my family and his still get along great and will forever, it is better like that for Lou's sake. 

Wanna hear car convo yesterday on the way from daycare to therapy.

Louis: Mom, do you think the baby will look like me?
Me: Im sure you will have some simularities, but not all the same.
Louis: Why?
Me: Cause you have the same Mommy but not the same Daddy as the baby.
Louis: We have the same Daddy, cause I have two Daddies.
Me: That is true but your Daddy Louis and I made you and Your Dustin and I made the baby.
Louis: How did you make me? With tools? 
Me: (In my head, yeah but none that you'd recognize,lol) No honey it was something a lil different.

Then I went on to carefully explain to him how babies are made without too much detail.
Then he says:

Louis: So by egg do you mean the same kind that Uncle Jason came out of?
Me: What?
Louis: Grandma said she didnt give birth to him that she sat on him and he hatched like a chicken egg.
Me: LMFAO Hysterically (gets on the phone with mom while driving)and she says: "I told him that like a year ago Candice, I was making fun of your brother in front him, she giggles."

So yeah, I thought it was funny.
